      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is so old school and just keeps telling me the same thing. it's such a hassle. i've been reading online that garlic is a natural blood thinner anyway. if i really ramped up the garlic to like 2-3 grams a day and drink the green juice every single morning, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as the warfarin? i just want to avoid the medicine if i can.",
